GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CadenceRhythm> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CadenceRhythm> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#CadenceRhythm> ;
    narr:childCount "20"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers prose-cadence observations on the founder's writing voice. The dominant register is **staccato compression**: short declarative punches ([snappy imperative repetition](narr:StyleObs_Cadence_1), [8-word subject-verb-object lines](narr:StyleObs_MicroTelltales), [un-hedged conviction anchors](narr:StyleObs_ShortPunchyDeclaratives) dated 2026-04-14), [verb-only/noun-only fragments](narr:StyleObs_1), and [deliberate long-then-short alternation](narr:StyleObs_SentenceLengthVariation) for rhythm. A second strong thread is **triadic structure** — rule-of-three lists for memorability ([what you know / how it's changed / IP](narr:StyleObs_RuleOfThree_1), [three scales/tools/outputs](narr:StyleObs_RuleOfThreeScales), [tricolons closing sections](narr:StyleObs_11), [scope-header three-beat](narr:StyleObs_ScopeHeaderStructure)). Punctuation cadence recurs: the [em-dash](narr:StyleObs_EmDashCadence) and the [→ arrow pipeline](narr:StyleObs_ArrowChaining). Brand stylization ([lowercase 'aswritten'](narr:StyleObs_3)), [analogy/simile](narr:StyleObs_Simile_1), [process enumeration](narr:StyleObs_ProcessEnumeration), and [iteration-velocity markers](narr:StyleObs_SkillEveryDay) round out the span. These are surface telltales, not a single thesis — each is one expand from its raw context.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_11> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_3> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_4> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ArrowChaining> ;
